    >
      <tr>
        <td align="center">
          <table
            width="750"
            cellpadding="0"
            cellspacing="0"
            style="
              background-color: #ffffff;
              border-radius: 0px;
              overflow: hidden;
              box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            "
          >
            <tr>
              <td
                style="
                  background-color: #000000;
                  padding: 50px 40px;
                  text-align: center;
                "
              >
                <div style="margin-bottom: 20px">
                  <img
                    src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dhdpnfvfn/image/upload/v1769745581/byte-beyond-persona-logo_novsd8.svg"
                    alt="Byte Beyond Persona Logo"
                    class="logo"
                    style="width: 400px; height: auto; display: inline-block"
                  />
                </div>
                <p
                  style="
                    margin: 20px 0 0;
                    font-size: 13px;
                    color: #ffffff;
                    text-transform: uppercase;
                    letter-spacing: 4px;
                    opacity: 0.8;
                    font-weight: 300;
                  "
                >
                  Account Deletion Confirmed
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 60px 50px">
                <h2
                  style="
                    margin: 0 0 24px;
                    font-size: 24px;
                    font-weight: 400;
                    color: #1a1a1a;
                    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
                    text-transform: uppercase;
                  "
                >
                  Hi
                  <strong>{{firstName}}</strong>,
                </h2>

                <p
                  style="
                    margin: 0 0 18px;
                    font-size: 16px;
                    line-height: 1.8;
                    color: #444444;
                    font-weight: 400;
                  "
                >
                  Akun Anda di Byte Beyond Persona telah berhasil dihapus sesuai
                  permintaan Anda.
                </p>

                <p
                  style="
                    margin: 0 0 24px;
                    font-size: 16px;
                    line-height: 1.8;
                    color: #444444;
                  "
                >
                  Terima kasih telah mempercayai kami dan menjadi bagian dari
                  komunitas Byte Beyond Persona. Kami menghargai waktu yang
                  telah Anda habiskan bersama kami.
                </p>

                <p
                  style="
                    margin: 0 0 32px;
                    font-size: 16px;
                    line-height: 1.8;
                    color: #444444;
                  "
                >
                  Jika Anda berubah pikiran di masa mendatang, kami akan dengan
                  senang hati menyambut Anda kembali.
                </p>

                <p
                  style="
                    margin: 0 0 40px;
                    font-size: 14px;
                    line-height: 1.6;
                    color: #888888;
                    border-left: 2px solid #00a86b;
                    padding-left: 20px;
                  "
                >
                  <em>If this action was not made by you, please contact support
                    immediately.</em>
                </p>

                <div
                  style="
                    margin: 50px auto 0;
                    width: 40px;
                    height: 1px;
                    background-color: #ffcc00;
                  "
                ></div>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 0 50px 50px; text-align: center">
                <p
                  style="
                    margin: 0;
                    font-size: 11px;
                    color: #bbbbbb;
                    text-transform: uppercase;
                    letter-spacing: 1px;
                    line-height: 1.8;
                  "
                >
                  Terima kasih telah mempercayai kami.<br />
                  <span style="font-size: 10px">Thank you for being with Byte
                    Beyond Persona.</span>
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
